= Secured

A plugin adding a layer of authority, identity, and security to the original
rails framework.

== Installation

  ruby script/plugin install ssh://deepserve.deepend.com/git/secured.git
  
== Usage

=== Prepare database

Generate and apply the migrations and models

  ruby script/generate secured
  rake db:migrate


